    "Name": "Barghest",
    "Details": "The -1T carries two ER Large Lasers that allow the Barghest to hit a target at up to five hundred and seventy meters. For medium to close range combat, the 'Mech carries a powerful LB-X Autocannon/20 that is capable of firing both standard ammunition and cluster rounds that act like 'Mech-sized shotgun shells. The 'Mech's simplicity is also a weakness, as the Barghest has only the two ER Large Lasers if the autocannon falls silent from a lack of ammunition or a jam.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Quad Mech</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>",
